{"id":"317145193_Adaptive_Output_Tracking_Backstepping_Sliding_Mode_Control_of_Nonlinear_Systems","abstract":"This paper considers the design of sliding mode control using a combined adaptive backstepping sliding mode control (SMC) algorithm for a class of nonlinear continuous uncertain processes which can be converted to a semi-parametric strict feedback form. The algorithm follows a systematic procedure for the design of dynamical adaptive SMC laws for the output of observable minimum phase nonlinear systems with matched and unmatched uncertainty. An existing sufficient condition for sliding is not needed by the new algorithm.","authors":["Ali Jafari Koshkouei","Alan S.I. Zinober"],"meta":["September 2000IFAC Proceedings Volumes (IFAC Papers-OnLine) 33(14):167-172","DOI:10.1016/S1474-6670(17)36223-7"],"references":["306314564_Adaptive_Backstepping_and_Sliding_Mode_Control_of_Uncertain_Nonlinear_Systems","306033851_Dynamical_Adaptive_Backstepping_Control_via_Symbolic_Computation","268355314_Adaptive_Sliding_Backstepping_Control_of_Nonlinear_Semi-Strict_Feedback_Form_Systems","266449713_A_symbolic_computation_toolbox_for_the_design_of_dynamical_adaptive_nonlinear_controllers","229911952_Dynamical_adaptive_sliding_mode_output_tracking_control_of_a_class_of_nonlinear_systems","3029637_Continuous_State_Feedback_Guaranteeing_Uniform_Ultimate_Boundedness_for_Uncertain_Dynamic_Systems","3029188_Continous_State_Feedback_Guaranteeing_Uniform_Ultimate_Boundedness_for_Uncertain_Dynamic_Systems","317309274_Tracking_Controllers_for_Systems_Linear_in_the_Unmeasured_States","243643717_Smooth_robust_adaptive_sliding_mode_control_of_manipulators_with_guaranteed_transient_response","237721218_Adaptive_Nonlinear_Control_without_Overparametrization","222776859_Tracking_Controllers_for_Systems_Linear_in_the_Unmeasured_States","3020929_Systematic_Design_of_Adaptive_Controllers_for_Feedback_Linearizable_Systems"]}